cs.LO, cs.DS, cs.CC, cs.PL, cs.AI

Reasoning: 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely category as the paper deals with a logic system extended with Presburger arithmetic. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is also likely as the paper presents an algorithm for solving the finite satisfiability problem of the logic. 
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is relevant as the paper proves NP-completeness of the logic. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) could be a possible category as the paper deals with a formal logic system. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is less likely but still possible as Presburger arithmetic is often used in AI applications such as automated planning and scheduling.
